---
---
<section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6 text-center bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 text-xs font-medium mb-8">
      <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-500"></span>
      Gratuito &middot; Open source &middot; Windows
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-950 tracking-tight leading-tight mb-6">
      Um assistente de IA<br />
      <span class="text-indigo-600">que roda na sua máquina</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed mb-10">
      Acesse seu filesystem, execute comandos no terminal e navegue na web — tudo através de uma conversa natural com a IA. Compatível com Claude, OpenAI e Ollama.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <a
        id="hero-download-btn"
        href="#download"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 px-7 py-3.5 bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white font-semibold rounded-xl transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-indigo-200 text-sm"
      >
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4" />
        </svg>
        Baixar para Windows
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/pierre-santos013/iac"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-3.5 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 text-gray-700 font-semibold rounded-xl border border-gray-200 transition-colors text-sm"
      >
        Ver no GitHub
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
